OL,3,COfcom announces 'game changing' new
OL,4,Crules to keep children safe online
OL,6,FOfcom CEO Dame Melanie Dawes said the
OL,7,Fmeasures will mean safer social media
OL,8,Ffeeds, as ITV News presenter Faye
OL,9,FBarker reports
OL,11,FOfcom has announced what it calls
OL,12,F"game-changing" new rules designed to
OL,13,Fkeep children safe online.
OL,15,FThe communications regulator, which
OL,16,Fnow also oversees online safety,
OL,17,Fpublished more than 40 measures which
OL,18,Fmake up the Protection of Children
OL,19,FCodes and Guidance on Thursday.
