OL,3,COfcom announces 'game changing' new
OL,4,Crules to keep children safe online
OL,6,FThe measures include requiring online
OL,7,Fplatforms to have robust age checks to
OL,8,Fstop children from accessing harmful
OL,9,Fcontent, to ensure that algorithms
OL,10,Fthat recommend content do not operate
OL,11,Fin a way that harms children, and to
OL,12,Fimplement more effective moderation
OL,13,Fsystems so that quick action is taken
OL,14,Fon harmful content.
OL,16,FOfcom says its priority is to protect
OL,17,Fchildren so they can enjoy the
OL,18,Fbenefits of being online, without
OL,19,Fexperiencing the potentially serious
OL,20,Fharms that exist in the online world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
