OL,3,COfcom announces 'game changing' new
OL,4,Crules to keep children safe online
OL,6,FOn Thursday, the regulator's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive called the changes a "reset"
OL,8,Ffor children online.
OL,10,FDame Melanie Dawes, continued: "They
OL,11,Fwill mean safer social media feeds
OL,12,Fwith less harmful and dangerous
OL,13,Fcontent, protections from being
OL,14,Fcontacted by strangers and effective
OL,15,Fage checks on adult content.
OL,17,F"Ofcom has been tasked with bringing
OL,18,Fabout a safer generation of children
OL,19,Fonline, and if companies fail to act
OL,20,Fthey will face enforcement."
