OL,3,COfcom announces 'game changing' new
OL,4,Crules to keep children safe online
OL,6,FThere is concern, however, that the
OL,7,Fnew Protection of Children Codes do
OL,8,Fnot go far enough.
OL,10,FDaisy Greenwell, who co-founded the
OL,11,Fgrassroots movement, Smartphone Free
OL,12,FChildhood, told ITV News: "This is a
OL,13,Fpositive step forward in building a
OL,14,Fdigital world that doesn't expose
OL,15,Fchildren to the sorts of harm we'd
OL,16,Fnever allow in the real world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
