OL,3,COfcom announces 'game changing' new
OL,4,Crules to keep children safe online
OL,6,F"But while this new Code is welcome,
OL,7,Fit also highlights how slowly the
OL,8,Fwheels of regulation turn compared to
OL,9,Fthe pace of technological change....
OL,10,FIn real life, no product, toy or
OL,11,Fdevice used by kids hits the market
OL,12,Fwithout extensive testing and proof of
OL,13,Fsafety.
OL,15,F"And yet our children are spending an
OL,16,Faverage of 35 hours a week on devices
OL,17,Fand platforms that have gone through
OL,18,Fno safety testing, and where
OL,19,Foverwhelming evidence points to
OL,20,Fserious harm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
