OL,6,FTech safety expert Lina Ghazal, who
OL,7,Fused to work at Meta and Ofcom and is
OL,8,Fnow Head of Regulatory and Public
OL,9,FAffairs at online safety provider
OL,10,FVerifymy, said: "With the regulator
