OL,3,COfcom announces 'game changing' new
OL,4,Crules to keep children safe online
OL,6,F"In 2025, the industry's top priority
OL,7,Fshould be creating safer, more
OL,8,Fsupportive online environments for
OL,9,Fchildren. The regulatory framework and
OL,10,Fthe technology to back it up already
OL,11,Fexist, so platforms have no excuse not
OL,12,Fto take immediate action."
OL,14,FSome commentators, like American
OL,15,Fsocial psychologist and author of the
OL,16,Fbestseller "The Anxious Generation,"
OL,17,FJonathan Haidt, have drawn a line
OL,18,Fdirectly between an increased use of
OL,19,Fsocial media and smartphones and a
OL,20,Frapid decline in the mental health of
OL,21,Fyoung people.
